  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "English Infant Care Teacher",
  "description": "<p>MapleBear Jurong Lakeside is expanding, and we are looking for passionate Infant Educarers to join our Jurong centre and grow with us.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities & Skills</strong></p><ul><li><p>Patient and sensitive to the needs of infants</p></li><li><p>Responsible and attentive to infants’ safety, health, and well-being</p></li><li><p>Strong communication skills to engage parents and caregivers</p></li><li><p>A team player who works well with colleagues</p></li><li><p>Well-organized with good time management skills</p></li></ul><p>You will be part of a dynamic team dedicated to nurturing and building meaningful connections with young learners.</p><p><strong>Education & Licensing Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Certificate in Infant Care (CIT), Advanced Certificate in Early Years (ACEY), Higher Certificate in Infant Care (HCIC), or equivalent</p></li><li><p>Diploma in Early Childhood Care & Education or Teaching; ACEY L1/L2 certified</p></li></ul><p><strong>Apply Now</strong><br />Be part of the MapleBear team and make a lasting impact on young learners’ growth.<br />Email or WhatsApp your resume to <strong>8512 5688</strong>.</p>",
